components.name: SioCoreDarkModeToggleComponent
components.templateData:
<ion-list inset="true">
  <ion-item lines="none" button>
    <sio-icon [name]="this.icon" slot="start"></sio-icon>
    <ion-toggle #darkmode_toggle (ionChange)="this.onChange($event)" slot="end"></ion-toggle>
    <label>{{ this.label | translate }}</label>
  </ion-item>
</ion-list>

components.name: SioCoreHeaderComponent
components.templateData:
<ion-header *ngIf="this.toolbar && !this.fullmode" collapse="fade" [translucent]="true" class="ion-no-border">
  <ion-toolbar [color]="this.color">
    <ion-buttons slot="start">
      <ng-container>
        <ion-menu-button *ngIf="this.menu"></ion-menu-button>
        <ion-back-button *ngIf="this.back"></ion-back-button>
      </ng-container>
    </ion-buttons>
    <ion-title>{{ this.title| translate }}</ion-title>
    <ion-buttons slot="end">
      <ng-content select="[slot='end']"> </ng-content>
    </ion-buttons>
  </ion-toolbar>
</ion-header>

components.name: SioCoreTabComponent
components.templateData:
<ion-tabs (ionTabsDidChange)="this.ionTabsDidChange(1)" (ionTabsWillChange)="this.ionTabsWillChange(1)">
  <ion-tab-bar *ngIf="this.position === 'bottom'" slot="bottom" [color]="this.color" class="ion-no-border">
    <ion-tab-button *ngFor="let item of sioCoreMenuState?.items | keyvalue" [tab]="item.value.url" [disabled]="false" 
      [download]="undefined">
      <ion-icon *ngIf="item.value.caption !== '--' && item.value.id < 6" [ios]="item.value.icon + '-outline'"
        [md]="item.value.icon + '-sharp'">
      </ion-icon>
      <ion-label *ngIf="item.value.caption !== '--' && item.value.id < 6">{{ (item.value.caption ? item.value.caption :
        'M_'+item.value.url!.replace('/',
        '_').toUpperCase()) |
        translate }}</ion-label>
      <ion-badge *ngIf="item.value.caption !== '--' && item.value.id < 6 && item.value.badge! > 0">{{ item.value.badge
        }}</ion-badge>
    </ion-tab-button>
  </ion-tab-bar>
  <ion-tab-bar *ngIf="this.position === 'top'" slot="top" [color]="this.color" class="ion-no-border top">
    <ion-tab-button *ngFor="let item of sioCoreMenuState?.items | keyvalue" [tab]="item.value.url" [disabled]="false" 
      [download]="undefined" layout="icon-start">
      <ion-icon *ngIf="item.value.caption !== '--' && item.value.id < 6" [ios]="item.value.icon + '-outline'"
        [md]="item.value.icon + '-sharp'">
      </ion-icon>
      <ion-label *ngIf="item.value.caption !== '--' && item.value.id < 6">{{ (item.value.caption ? item.value.caption :
        'M_'+item.value.url!.replace('/',
        '_').toUpperCase()) |
        translate }}</ion-label>
      <ion-badge *ngIf="item.value.caption !== '--' && item.value.id < 6 && item.value.badge! > 0">{{ item.value.badge
        }}</ion-badge>
    </ion-tab-button>
  </ion-tab-bar>
</ion-tabs>
